item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - No Rap Versions of "Knock You Down" and "Turnin Me On" by Keri Hilson
item.description:
Hello everyone,

I'm still searching for a No Rap Version of Keri Hilson's "Knock You Down". I heard a version once on New York's WPLJ radio stations. The version eliminated Kanye's rap and included the bridge from the Album Version (which was cut by the regular Radio Edit). Does anyone have a copy of it or a No Rap Version of "Knock You Down"?

I also saw on Discogs that a No Rap Version of the song "Turnin' Me On" also exists. Does anyone have a copy?

It would be greatly appreciated.
